commit 83babcae7a23045dd5c2c7ab4ddb9e8f3c3145d0
Author: quivent <quivent@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Wed Apr 8 16:39:37 2026 -0400

    qwen35: add MTP draft-graph path mirroring qwen3next
    
    Adds build_mtp_head and the LLM_GRAPH_TYPE_MTP early-return branch
    to llm_build_qwen35 so the dispatcher in llama_context::mtp_graph_compute
    can run the NextN head for Qwen3.5 models with nextn_predict_layers > 0.
    
    The head follows the MLX reference in ~/mlx-fork/fused_gdn.py MTPHead:
    enorm(embed), hnorm(hidden), concat [embed, hidden] (embed-first is the
    critical eh_proj order), eh_proj down to n_embd, one gated self-attention
    block with q/k norms and RoPE at pos 0, dense SiLU MLP, shared_head_norm,
    then shared_head_head projection to vocab.
    
    Qwen3.5 MTP layer 64 is dense full-attention, so the FFN uses
    layer.ffn_{gate,up,down} and attention uses layer.w{q,k,v,o} with the *2
    gating factor on wq. Exports res->t_mtp_prev_hidden_in and
    res->t_mtp_pos_zero_in for dispatcher upload.
    
    TODO(dedupe): share with llm_build_qwen3next::build_mtp_head.

